.IP \(bu 2
\fIgem\fP \-\- RubyGems
.IP \(bu 2
\fImas\fP \-\- Mac App Store CLI
.IP \(bu 2
\fInpm\fP \-\- Node.js Package Manager
.IP \(bu 2
\fIpip\fP \-\- Pip Installs Packages
.IP \(bu 2
\fIsystem\fP \-\- macOS Software Update (\fBsoftwareupdate(8)\fP)
.UNINDENT
